verbose_text: The band maximum of linearly coordinated CO on Pt-Y-NH 3 is present at 2077 cm -1 shown in green in Figure XREF_FIG b, in accordance with earlier studies reporting band maxima of 2083 cm -1 for Pt nanoparticles of < = 1 nm supported on H-Y zeolite.51 The band maximum of Pt-Y / A-NH 3 is present at 2070 cm -1, that is lower than for Pt-Y-NH 3 but significantly higher than for Pt-A-Cl.
